description:
Get your PEOPLE fix on your tablet with this celebrity news app.  If you currently subscribe to PEOPLE magazine in print, you can access the tablet edition FREE! Each week you'll experience the regular features of the PEOPLE magazine you love, but now you can enjoy your entertainment news in a whole new way. 
You’ll get: 
- DOUBLE the number of Star Tracks pics, and bonus, tablet-only, celebrity photo galleries throughout the issue
- Exclusive, behind-the-scenes star videos 
- Movie trailers, TV previews, song samples and other entertainment extras 
- Instant breaking news updates on top stories throughout the entire week 
You can read and store as many issues as you’d like in your library.  Download the app today and get instant access to the latest issue. 

Note: By downloading this application, you agree to the End User License Agreement (including the Privacy Policy and Terms of Service referenced therein) which can be viewed by going to www.timeinc.net/subs/pe-eula.html or clicking the “Support” button on this page.  

Seller: TI Media Solutions Inc.
